{"tid":1518933,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"無 私 無 畏 即 自 由","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T06:23:49.000Z","uid":41080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7b56f28390cfa4aac9714b0b98f89f9b913dc5","tid":1518933,"uid":41080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"2014年，《明報》前總編輯劉進圖被斬，身中六刀危殆入院，甦醒後道：無私無畏即自由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你對831有任何懷疑自己既想法，請你在心中默念 ： <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">無 私 無 畏 即 自 由</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140302/52240187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140302%2F52240187&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiqb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=37552dce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140302%2F52240187&h=ec7aab70\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20140302/52240187</a><br />\n<br />\n// 做完手術甦醒後，我在病床上想起在港大讀書時見過的一張大字報，上面寫著兩句，「真理在胸筆在手，無私無畏即自由」，傳媒要堅守真道、真理、正義，運用手中的筆，才可以發揮真正的影響力，而人們無私無畏，就能享有自由。 //"},{"pid":"6ebf964f34b12f082c5558b94a58f2aade6a1628","tid":1518933,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:46:11.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a 